{"tid":52229,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我最主要就係想指一阿記輸波的最大原因．．．","createTime":"2016-12-24T01:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T04:58:39.000Z","uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c8820f839c77bdf90949e91bf2c75b6094c1e98","tid":52229,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"我最主要就係想指一阿記輸波的最大原因，當然球員和教練都有一定的責任，但我認為最大的問題是反阿的那幫人，我上社交網站上看到，他們日日都在評擊阿記，是阿記輸波的關鍵！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dg87i.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDg87i.gif&h=dd5b2806&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果不喜歡阿記的話，就請支持其他球隊，為什麼日日都想希望阿記輸波？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yz87.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yz87.gif&h=eff61a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿記這兩季的成績大幅下滑，都是因為那班反阿的7頭日日在咀咒阿記輸波，而最不幸的是，竟然連個天都幫埋佢地，搞到阿記打到咁差。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90YU4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90YU4.gif&h=b4a840c0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉！我明白有批評才有進步，但現在的阿記，真的很需要各隊球迷的支持，才能重震雄風！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cT9qN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcT9qN.gif&h=b1834d90&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請停止對阿記的批評或咀咒，並關閉其有關的專頁和網站！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cm83h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcm83h.gif&h=c21b1367&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿記成績下滑最要主原因是反阿人士不斷的干擾，如果他們的不停止反阿行動的話，那就消滅他們吧！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4Bec.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4Bec.gif&h=012b88cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只有這樣做才可以令阿記做番一隊英超BIG 4<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49Fpr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49Fpr.gif&h=a07ba948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b52c3af697a7b4f2e12d3ff46128e310f47749","tid":52229,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00dd98789c923424277d703a35ce4491f5aceac","tid":52229,"uid":13874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"咪第四左囉"},{"pid":"2c06ad3597b747c8ea7f70bec942bbdc651abb56","tid":52229,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"雲加廢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127c349ef49ed8e588cfcddc5e6c359f7ede992a","tid":52229,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}